                                    <p class="text-muted">we have won alot of championes but the championeslega championes was very fantastic ,because the team face some difcults before wen the championes </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-inverted">
                            <div class="timeline-image">
                                <img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="img/about/2.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-panel">
                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4>March 2020</h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">local championes</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">the team played all matches in lega and has won in alot of them and won in laliega </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="timeline-image">
                                <img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="img/about/3.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-panel">
                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4>December 2020</h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">King cub championes</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">the team played a final match with enmy and won ,the result 3-1 and take the championes and celebrate with fans </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-inverted">
                            <div class="timeline-image">
                                <img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="img/about/4.jpg" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-panel">
                                <div class="timeline-heading">
                                    <h4>July 2020</h4>
                                    <h4 class="subheading">Our Player</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="timeline-body">
                                    <p class="text-muted">we have agreat team contanis some famous player like ronaldo ,zidan and alot of local players they won in alot of chamipones befor</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-inverted">
                            <div class="timeline-image">
                                <h4>
                                    Be Part
                                    <br>Of Our
                                    <br>Story!
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team -->
    <section class="bg-light" id="team">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">Our Amazing Team</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">because we are the top and our team is very profisional</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img class="mx-auto rounded-circle" src="~/image/r4.jpg" alt="">
                        <h4>Our Championes</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">alot of championes</p>
                        <p class="text-muted"></p>
                        <ul class="list-inline social-buttons">
                            <li class="list-inline-item">
                                <a href="#">
